  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "content": "### How To Read\n- **Search Throughput (5m Rate)**: 每秒搜索请求数，按搜索模式、执行路径和状态拆分。\n- **Provider Latency P95**: 过去 5 分钟内，95% 的搜索 provider 调用在该耗时内完成。\n- **Source Imports (Last 1h)**: 最近 1 小时导入成功或跳过的来源数量。\n- **Async Job Outcomes (Last 1h)**: 最近 1 小时搜索/后台任务成功或失败次数。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Read",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "每秒搜索请求数，按搜索模式、执行路径和状态拆分。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (mode, execution, status) (rate(notebooklm_search_requests_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{mode}} / {{execution}} / {{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Search Throughput (5m Rate)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "搜索 provider 的 P95 延迟，单位毫秒。只看 success 曲线最能反映真实服务时延。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, provider, mode, status) (rate(notebooklm_search_provider_duration_ms_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{provider}} / {{mode}} / {{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Provider Latency P95",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "最近 1 小时来源导入结果。`imported` 表示真正创建了文章，`skipped` 通常表示去重命中。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "single" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (source_type, result) (increase(notebooklm_source_import_total[1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{source_type}} / {{result}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Source Imports (Last 1h)",
      "type": "barchart"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "最近 1 小时异步任务结果。重点看失败曲线是否抬头，以及 `search_deep` / `article_ingest` 是否积压。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (job_type, status) (increase(notebooklm_jobs_total{job_type=~\"search_deep|article_ingest|article_reindex|maintenance_cleanup\"}[1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{job_type}} / {{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Async Job Outcomes (Last 1h)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "10s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "style": "dark",
  "tags": ["notebooklm", "search"],
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "timezone": "browser",
